AHHH i likee it likee thattt she workin that backk i dunno how to acttt!! lmaoo .. waitin for my mom for like 2 hourss.. makin ur ass clean n NO i dont wanna see no pictures until u finish cleanin ur room!  haha those pictures from JAMAICA!! lmao.. damn we had  great night.. lol, then yahh i waited for my mom to get me but linda ended up gettin me n we had to drop francina off at BoneYard cuz she was goin home with Sophiaa.. then i came home, went on the computer n stuff .. talked to D =) but that was really gay so i dont wanna talk about it ..  i swear man, i wish he never sayd that stuff to me =*( .. me danny george n andrea went into a chat room..damn man those ppl were sendin us pictures n all that stuff.. haha DONT ARREST ME PLEASE!! lol that shyt was funny .. then i got out of the chat or wahtever n didnt feel like talkin anymore bcuz once again i cant sleep .. so me n emma talked on the phone ALL NIGHT probly till like 5:00 .. wow man we like talked bout a lot of shit .. that was probly the best conversation me n her ever day in the past..week .. lol, well that about it so ill write again later .. <3

hah i was too tired to update this but ill try to recap on what happened..hmmm well on sunday nichole came over .. me n tina picked her up then we went to pick up emma =) we all chilled at my house laughed n all that good stuff then we dropped emma off around 9:30 ish..then me n nichole chilled outside..lmao tryin to run away from tina n shpresa.. we knocked on the kitchen window n they were soo scared so we had to hide behind the pool..then got up but noone was there lmaoo that shyt was funny..then nichole left around 11:30..me n tina chilled in my room talked n stuff..that was basically it..then on monday i went to emmas house =D tina dropped me n shpresa off there..well actually she stayed too..lol we chilled there then we went to Tinas to get her stuff n have her take a shower cuz she hasnt in like 2 weeks..(kinda sick lol) took her bout like 5 yrs to get ready.. it was good that her n her sis reunited again 0=)..then we left n came back to emmas.. we had renatas lil celebration birthday party..which was really fun..we danced in the basement me n emma doin them a mary-kate and ashley show to their twins song (hah i love them)..lmao that was really funny then we all danced to Bashkimmiiiii!! lol Jk i love you <3 .. soo yeah we ended up wakin up att like 1? lol..chilled got ready for the day .. the fam was gunna go to tha beach but they ended up not going cuz company came.. me n emma waited for them to leave then we walked to McDonalds .. =P then we walked to KFC to see somethin but that was dumb so we used that place to use the potty =X lol .. walked behind K-mart cuz we dont like the workers there anymore ..lol then came back home..her grandma was just there so we chilled until her parents came..put away the groceries n stuff.. then we went outside with them..played with Isabella! aww shes so damn cute! =)..then laterish me n emma took bella to tha park .. her mom came by there so we were all swingin lmao..i almost killed myself jumpin off tha swing.. n walkin on the woodchips lol then tha park guy came n kicked us out cuz their park closes at 9? which is pretty gay ..lol we ended up walkin back home with dameon n his friend + emmas mom .. seen ash on tha way =) .. then this 1 physco guy on the bike got hit by a car cuz this other physco hit him..=X wow that shyt was fukin scary.. im scared of their neighborhood.. u never know when a car will hit u cuz u were accused of not stoppin at the stop sign but really u did stop?? lmao yah i jus confused tha hell out of myself right there lol .. anyywayy so we went back home..blahh blahh chilled in roberts room n emmas room/ read sum lyrics n got sum cute shyt there..then read quotes online..francina n tina ended up commin over there round 11 so i had to leave =( .. they stayed for a while cuz we were gettin amused by bella!! lol .. thenn yah i left..came home n jus chilled, it was really cold in my room so i actually wore a sweatshirt in MY room ..lol (( comfy sweater 0=) )).. anddd yah now im juss chillen n listenin to music..bout to go to bed cuz noones on..
